message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper discusses an approach to question answering using sequence to sequence learning, which is a common technique in natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.LG) to generate answers. Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language generation (cs.NE), which are relevant sub-categories in the context of question answering.
